mean_en: If you misread something that has been written or printed, you look at it and think that it says something that it does not say
sentence: The father misread the signal and thought the baby was crying because he was hungry.
sentence_trans: 父亲误解了信号，以为宝宝哭是因为肚子饿了。
word_etyma: mis错误，坏 ＋ read读 → misread读错
